========
gpiozero
========

.. image:: https://badge.fury.io/gh/gpiozero%2Fgpiozero.svg
    :target: https://badge.fury.io/gh/gpiozero%2Fgpiozero
    :alt: Source code on GitHub

.. image:: https://badge.fury.io/py/gpiozero.svg
